@startuml
title State Diagram - AttendanceReport Generation And Export

[*] --> FILTER_SELECTED : administrator selects optional filters

FILTER_SELECTED --> GENERATING : click Generate Report
GENERATING --> GENERATED_EMPTY : no matching report lines
GENERATING --> GENERATED_WITH_LINES : report lines created
GENERATING --> FAILED : generation error

GENERATED_EMPTY --> FILTER_SELECTED : change filters
GENERATED_EMPTY --> GENERATED_EMPTY : export blocked\n"Cannot export an empty report."

GENERATED_WITH_LINES --> EXPORTED : export CSV
GENERATED_WITH_LINES --> FILTER_SELECTED : generate another report

FAILED --> FILTER_SELECTED : fix filters or data

EXPORTED --> GENERATED_WITH_LINES : report remains available

note right of FILTER_SELECTED
Filters are optional.
Null or empty means unrestricted.
end note

note right of GENERATED_WITH_LINES
overallPerformancePercentage is calculated
as average ReportLine attendance percentage.
end note

note right of EXPORTED
CSV includes metadata, conclusion,
overall performance, and report lines.
end note

@enduml
